chive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASt1ISRvQ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 185, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8694834, "raw_content": "A religion seeks truth, encourages debate, and allows free will. \nA cult demands blind obedience, punishes dissent, and seeks to dominate all aspects of life. Islam fits the cult definition perfectly:\n- Absolute authority (Muhammad is the \"perfect man,\" his words are infallible).\n- Us vs. Them mentality (Dar al-Islam vs. Dar al-Harb\u2014House of War).\n- Punishment for leaving (Apostasy = death).\n- Control over daily life (Prayer 5x a day, dietary laws, dress codes, etc.).\n\nNo other major religion executes people for leaving. But Islam does. That\u2019s not a religion\u2014that\u2019s a cult with a billion members.\nThe West is funding its own destruction\nWorst of all? We\u2019re letting them in. Western leaders bend over backward to accommodate Islam, while ignoring the genocide of Christians in the Middle East. We\u2019re told to \"respect\" a belief system that hates our guts and wants to replace our laws with Sharia.\nWhy are we importing people who believe in stoning women?\nWhy are we funding mosques that preach jihad?\nWhy are we allowing Sharia courts to operate in our countries?Islam is a Threat\u2014and we should act like It.\nIslam isn\u2019t just another religion. It\u2019s a \"civilizational jihad\"\u2014a slow-motion invasion designed to replace Western culture with Islamic rule. And if we don\u2019t wake up, we\u2019ll be living under Sharia before we know it.\n\nSo ask yourself:\n- Do you want your daughters wearing burqas?\n- Do you want your sons executed for \"blasphemy\"?\n- Do you want your country ruled by medieval theocrats?\n\nIf not, it\u2019s time to stop pretending Islam is just \"another faith.\" \nIt\u2019s a cult of conquest, and it\u2019s coming for us all.", "author": "NSFW_PORN_ONLY", "created": 1782240869113, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "E-dantes", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Islam is a Cult, Not a Religion", "last_comment_created": 1782262606493, "content": "<p>A religion seeks truth, encourages debate, and allows free will.\nA cult demands blind obedience, punishes dissent, and seeks to dominate all aspects of life. Islam fits the cult definition perfectly:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Absolute authority (Muhammad is the &quot;perfect man,&quot; his words are infallible).</li>\n<li>Us vs. Them mentality (Dar al-Islam vs. Dar al-Harb\u2014House of War).</li>\n<li>Punishment for leaving (Apostasy = death).</li>\n<li>Control over daily life (Prayer 5x a day, dietary laws, dress codes, etc.).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>No other major religion executes people for leaving. But Islam does. That\u2019s not a religion\u2014that\u2019s a cult with a billion members.\nThe West is funding its own destruction\nWorst of all? We\u2019re letting them in. Western leaders bend over backward to accommodate Islam, while ignoring the genocide of Christians in the Middle East. We\u2019re told to &quot;respect&quot; a belief system that hates our guts and wants to replace our laws with Sharia.\nWhy are we importing people who believe in stoning women?\nWhy are we funding mosques that preach jihad?\nWhy are we allowing Sharia courts to operate in our countries?Islam is a Threat\u2014and we should act like It.\nIslam isn\u2019t just another religion. It\u2019s a &quot;civilizational jihad&quot;\u2014a slow-motion invasion designed to replace Western culture with Islamic rule. And if we don\u2019t wake up, we\u2019ll be living under Sharia before we know it.</p>\n<p>So ask yourself:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Do you want your daughters wearing burqas?</li>\n<li>Do you want your sons executed for &quot;blasphemy&quot;?</li>\n<li>Do you want your country ruled by medieval theocrats?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If not, it\u2019s time to stop pretending Islam is just &quot;another faith.&quot;\nIt\u2019s a cult of conquest, and it\u2019s coming for us all.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 27, "score_up": 185, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2069581344401989741", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASt1JZTXC", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 54, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "apu", "id": 8695386, "raw_content": "", "author": "DCSucks", "created": 1782264697863, "profile_picture": "HROqPiS20z4h", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Brudermond", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASt1JZTXC.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/omoelerinjare1/status/2069581344401989741?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Ashamed of nothing. Offended by everything. ", "last_comment_created": 1782278137065, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 54, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 4, "created": 1782261618000, "i